Suzanne Delvé https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suzanne_Delv%C3%A9 0 Suzanne Delvé (1892–1986) was a French film actress. While most of her roles were during the silent era, she also appeared in a few sound films such as Maurice Tourneur's Accused, Stand Up! (1930).
